 P2y.jp  https://p2y.jp VTuber最新消息2024 年 2 月 6 日星期二 10:48:18 +0000贾每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.4.3 https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-logo_2023_150x150-32x32.png P2y.jp https://p2y.jp 32 32 166157578
 VTuber Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型“Dokibird”订阅人数迅速增加https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/ https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/#respondp2y_admin Tue, 06 Feb 2024 10:13:59 +0000 VTuberバーチャルDokibirdNIJISANJI EN(新)Selen Tatsuki(セレン龍月)YouTuberにじさんじプロジェクトチャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber個人勢 https://p2y.jp/?p=114169 <p>这次，VTuber Selen Tatsuki（Selen Tatsuki/隶属：NIJISANJI EN（新）/2月5日被ANYCOLOR Inc.取消的合同）表演者/声优[…]</p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/">VTuber Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模型“Dokibird”频道订阅者迅速增加</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>此次<strong>Dokibird</strong>官方YouTube频道的订阅人数，据说是VTuber Selen <strong>Tatsuki</strong>的表演者/声音模特（所属：NIJISANJI EN（新）/于2月5日由ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd.终止） ，已公布。经证实，该数字正在迅速增加。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>该信息包括真实性尚未确认的信息。一旦事实得到证实，我们将立即更新这篇文章。</strong> </p></blockquote><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="674" data-attachment-id="114173" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/dokibird-supposed-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-has-a-spike-in-youtube-subscribers/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024" data-image-description="&lt;p>;Dokibird&lt;/p>;
" data-image-caption="&lt;p>;Dokibird&lt;/p>;
" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dokibird_youtube_channel_february_6_2024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-114173"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Dokibird（截至2024年2月6日18:40）</figcaption></figure><p></p><p> 2月5日，运营NIJISANJI EN的公司ANYCOLOR对据称是Dokibird的表演者/声音模特的Seren Ryugetsu发出了投诉，称“<em>多次违反合同并在SNS上发布误导性虚假信息”。 &#39;据宣布，由于他的行为，合同将被终止</em>。</p><p>之后，Dokibird在他的X（Twitter）账户上宣布，他将于2月8日10:00开始进行“回归直播”。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="99ZPbZEwZb"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/">ANYCOLOR公司NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Selen Tatsuki的合同被取消</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 取消了 NIJISANJI EN（新）所属 VTuber Selen Tatsuki 的合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/embed/#?secret=3lFgUSbb19#?secret=99ZPbZEwZb" data-secret="99ZPbZEwZb" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="UMrfDb60K7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/alleged-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-dokibird-to-return-streaming-on-february-8/">据称是VTuber Selen Tatsuki的表演者/声优模特的人将于2月8日进行“回归分配”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Selen Tatsuki的表演者/声优模特将于2月8日进行‘回归配发’” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/alleged-actor-of-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-dokibird-to-return-streaming-on-february-8/embed/#?secret=PVw4GXnIcQ#?secret=UMrfDb60K7" data-secret="UMrfDb60K7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【我的归来】大家又回来了【Dokibird】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/J2YmJL0PX5M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="zqkoh65c2250673957" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
